2011-03-29  Sam Weinig  <sam@webkit.org>

        Reviewed by Anders Carlsson.

        Use LocalizedStrings.h as a bottleneck for localized strings instead of
        using UI_STRING.

        * UIProcess/API/mac/WKView.mm:
